  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "A Japan-only release of SimCity 2000 for the Nintendo 64 on January 30, 1998, produced and published by Imagineer Co., Ltd.\n\nIt featured some additional features, mainly mini-games, a dating game, TV to replace the newspaper, horse races and monster breeding, among others, all of them in 3D. A few new \"natural\" disasters were also included, most of them being giant monster attacks (players were able to use their monster to fight against them).",
